## Import Libraries
```python
import pandas as pd
import numpy as np
from pathlib import Path
import re
```

---

## Load Dataset
```python
root = Path("..")
raw_path = root / "data" / "raw_sales_data.csv"
clean_path = root / "cleaned" / "clean_sales_data.csv"

df = pd.read_csv(raw_path)
df.head()
```

